  <span id="freeText10687070705746073883" style="display:none">2.5 stars rounded up. Lots of potential with this story but some things were pretty obvious early on. I don't think the FBI would be so oblivious as the book implies. It was very hard to be vested in the lead character as she seemed pretty oblivious at times, undeveloped and apparently doesn't touch base with anyone outside of her boss. </span>
